cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.SI 

The paper proposes a fairness-enhancing dimensionality reduction algorithm using PCA. This falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence, specifically in the subfield of dimensionality reduction. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper uses empirical studies on different datasets, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and security and privacy (cs.CR) aspects. Finally, the paper also discusses the convergence analysis of the proposed algorithm, which falls under the sub-category of systems and control (cs.SI).
